    <header>
      <h1><a href="/anything">Anything You Want cartoons</a></h1>
      <p class="postdate">Length: <strong>16 minutes.</strong> Date recorded: 2011-07</p>
    </header>
    <p><strong>Philosophies on life and business, 7 chapters from my book, turned into short little animations.</strong></p>

<p>
Besides books, I'm a fan of movies, comic books, and animation. I love how the combination of visual and oral storytelling is so gripping.<br>
<br>
So when I was releasing my own book in July 2011, I hired a great animator - Marvin Te from http://www.plainlysimplestudios.com/ - and we worked together to make these 7 videos.<br>
<br>
I hope to keep doing new videos like this for future essays, too. I really love the format.<br>
<br>
If the videos are not showing, below, you can also see them at http://vimeo.com/album/1660848 or http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLCDDBA84EFA4061D1
</p>
